sub_title: Bilingual copywriter, editor & translator (English/Dutch), freelancer, language trainer
summary:
Skilled (content) writer, editor and translator with a passion for languages! 
My forte is writing for your target audience, and with the intended purpose firmly in mind. Writing short copy, long copy, newsletters, blogs or other online content (naturally keeping SEO in mind) about any subject, gets my pulse racing! I am a native speaker of both Dutch and English, so I am a natural communicator in both languages. 
I have extensive professional experience in Government, ICT, Sales and Publishing, amongst other fields, with a TESOL Cert IV from Teach International and a Business Bachelor from HAN University.
As a freelancer through my company BizEnglish, I write, translate, create, coach and support professionals and companies. I am an enthusiastic connector, motivator and communicator who believes in empowering people.
